---
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>FlagLint — Audit LaunchDarkly flag debt. Migrate to OpenFeature safely.</title>
  <meta name="description" content="FlagLint is a free, open-source CLI that audits LaunchDarkly Node.js SDK usage, previews safe OpenFeature migrations, and enforces the boundary in CI.">
  <meta property="og:title" content="FlagLint — Audit LaunchDarkly flag debt. Migrate to OpenFeature safely.">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Free, open-source CLI for auditing LaunchDarkly Node.js SDK usage, previewing safe OpenFeature migrations, and enforcing the boundary in CI.">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://flaglint.dev">
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="FlagLint">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://flaglint.dev/og.svg">
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
  <meta name="twitter:site" content="@flaglintdev">
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://flaglint.dev">
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" sizes="any">
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="96x96" href="/favicon-96.png">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32.png">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon-16.png">
  <link rel="manifest" href="/site.webmanifest">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style is:global>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --bg: #080a0a;
      --surface: #101313;
      --surface-raised: #171b1b;
      --surface-soft: #0d1117;
      --border: #26302d;
      --border-strong: #35443e;
      --text: #f2f5f3;
      --muted: #b3bcb8;
      --subtle: #7f8b86;
      --accent: #00d97e;
      --accent-soft: rgba(0, 217, 126, 0.13);
      --warning: #f2b84b;
      --danger: #ff6b6b;
      --radius: 8px;
      --shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.36);
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 18% 10%, rgba(0, 217, 126, 0.08), transparent 26%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #080a0a 0%, #0b0d0d 48%, #080a0a 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: -1;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.035) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.035) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 40px 40px;
      mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #000 0%, transparent 88%);
    }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    a:focus-visible, button:focus-visible {
      outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
      outline-offset: 3px;
    }
    code, pre { font-family: "SF Mono", "Cascadia Code", "Fira Code", ui-monospace, monospace; }
    nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
      background: rgba(8, 10, 10, 0.86);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    }
    .nav-inner {
      max-width: 1180px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      min-height: 64px;
      padding: 0 24px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }
    .logo span { color: var(--accent); }
    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 22px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }
    .github-btn {
      border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      color: var(--text);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    }
    main { display: block; }
    section { padding: 84px 24px; }
    .section-inner {
      max-width: 1180px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .section-kicker {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .section-heading {
      font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 46px);
      line-height: 1.12;
      letter-spacing: 0;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .section-copy {
      max-width: 760px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 17px;
    }
    .hero {
      padding: 96px 24px 72px;
    }
    .hero-grid {
      max-width: 1180px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 56px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .hero-grid > *,
    .proof-grid > *,
    .ci-example > *,
    [aria-label="Before and after FlagLint architecture"] > * {
      min-width: 0;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(38px, 4.2vw, 58px);
      line-height: 1.06;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .hero-sub {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 19px;
      max-width: 680px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .command-card {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      background: var(--surface-soft);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 12px 14px;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 8px 0 24px;
      max-width: 100%;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
    .cta-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 42px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 14px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #02100a;
    }
    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.035);
      color: var(--text);
      border-color: var(--border);
    }
    .proof-shell {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.04), rgba(255,255,255,0.02));
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .terminal-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    }
    .dots { display: flex; gap: 7px; }
    .dot { width: 11px; height: 11px; border-radius: 50%; }
    .dot.red { background: #ff5f57; }
    .dot.yellow { background: #febc2e; }
    .dot.green { background: #28c840; }
    .term-version {
      color: var(--subtle);
      font-size: 12px;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .terminal-body {
      padding: 18px;
      background: #0d1117;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
    .terminal-body pre {
      color: #d8e2dd;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      min-width: 560px;
      white-space: pre;
    }
    .green { color: var(--accent); }
    .amber { color: var(--warning); }
    .red { color: var(--danger); }
    .muted { color: var(--subtle); }
    .grid-3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 34px;
    }
    .grid-2 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 34px;
    }
    .card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .card h3 {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }
    .card p, .card li {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .card ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }
    .card li::before {
      content: "";
      display: inline-block;
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      margin-right: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent);
      vertical-align: 2px;
    }
    .workflow {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 0;
      margin-top: 36px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--surface);
    }
    .workflow-step {
      padding: 28px;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .workflow-step:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .step-num {
      display: inline-flex;
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      color: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 50%;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .mini-code {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 14px;
      background: #0d1117;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 12px;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
    .proof-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.92fr) minmax(0, 1.08fr);
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 34px;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .proof-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .proof-card h3 {
      padding: 18px 18px 0;
      font-size: 17px;
    }
    .proof-card p {
      padding: 6px 18px 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .proof-card pre {
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding: 18px;
      background: #0d1117;
      color: #d8e2dd;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
    .scope-table {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 34px;
    }
    .scope-label {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .ci-example {
      margin-top: 30px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .note {
      margin-top: 14px;
      color: var(--subtle);
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .docs-cta {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,217,126,0.08), rgba(0,0,0,0));
    }
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 28px 24px;
      color: var(--subtle);
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .footer-inner {
      max-width: 1180px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 18px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }
    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hero-grid, .proof-grid, .ci-example { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero { padding-top: 72px; }
      .grid-3, .scope-table, .workflow { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .workflow-step { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
      .workflow-step:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
      .nav-links a:not(.github-btn):not(.nav-search) { display: none; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 680px) {
      section { padding: 64px 18px; }
      .hero { padding: 68px 18px 56px; }
      .nav-links a:not(.github-btn):not(.nav-search) { display: none; }
      .nav-inner { padding: 0 18px; }
      .cta-row .btn { width: 100%; }
      .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .terminal-body { padding: 14px; }
      .terminal-body pre { font-size: 12px; min-width: 480px; }
      .command-card { width: 100%; }
      .search-label, .nav-search kbd { display: none; }
    }

    /* ── Light mode ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    [data-theme="light"] {
      --bg: #f8fafb;
      --surface: #ffffff;
      --surface-raised: #f0f4f7;
      --surface-soft: #eef2f5;
      --border: #d1dbe3;
      --border-strong: #b0c0cc;
      --text: #0f1a14;
      --muted: #3d5a4a;
      --subtle: #6b8a7a;
      --accent: #007a49;
      --accent-soft: rgba(0, 122, 73, 0.10);
      --shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
    }
    [data-theme="light"] body {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f0fdf6 0%, #f8fafb 30%, #f8fafb 100%);
    }
    [data-theme="light"] body::before {
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
    }
    [data-theme="light"] nav {
      background: rgba(248,250,251,0.92);
      border-bottom-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    [data-theme="light"] .github-btn {
      color: var(--text);
    }
    [data-theme="light"] .proof-shell {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff, #f8fafb);
    }
    [data-theme="light"] .terminal-body {
      background: #1a1f2e;
    }

    /* ── Theme toggle ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .theme-toggle {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2px;
      background: var(--surface-raised);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 2px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .theme-btn {
      background: none;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 4px 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-family: inherit;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      transition: background 0.1s, color 0.1s;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .theme-btn.active,
    .theme-btn:hover {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
    }
    [data-theme="light"] .theme-btn.active,
    [data-theme="light"] .theme-btn:hover {
      color: #fff;
    }

    /* ── Search button ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .nav-search {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      background: var(--surface-raised);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 5px 10px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color 0.15s, color 0.15s;
      white-space: nowrap;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .nav-search:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      color: var(--text);
    }
    .nav-search kbd {
      font-size: 11px;
      background: var(--surface-soft);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 3px;
      padding: 1px 4px;
      font-family: inherit;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
  </style>
  <script>(function(){var s=localStorage.getItem('flaglint-theme')||'dark';var r=s==='auto'?(window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches?'dark':'light'):s;document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme',r);})();</script>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "SoftwareApplication",
  "name": "FlagLint",
  "description": "Open-source CLI that inventories direct LaunchDarkly Node.js SDK calls, generates safe OpenFeature migration diffs, and enforces the OpenFeature boundary in CI.",
  "url": "https://flaglint.dev",
  "downloadUrl": "https://www.npmjs.com/package/flaglint",
  "softwareVersion": "0.6.0",
  "operatingSystem": "Node.js 20+",
  "applicationCategory": "DeveloperApplication",
  "offers": {
    "@type": "Offer",
    "price": "0",
    "priceCurrency": "USD"
  },
  "author": {
    "@type": "Person",
    "name": "Krishan Sharma",
    "url": "https://github.com/flaglint"
  },
  "license": "https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT",
  "codeRepository": "https://github.com/flaglint/flaglint"
}
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <nav>
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a class="logo" href="/">Flag<span>Lint</span></a>
      <div class="nav-links" aria-label="Primary navigation">
        <a href="/docs/cli/audit">Audit</a>
        <a href="/docs/quickstart">Quickstart</a>
        <a href="/docs/tutorials/migrate-a-node-service">Migration</a>
        <a href="/docs/integrations/github-actions">CI</a>
        <a href="/docs/reference/supported-scope">Scope</a>
        <a href="/blog/">Blog</a>
        <a href="/docs/" class="nav-search" id="nav-search-btn" title="Search docs (⌘K)" aria-label="Search documentation">
          <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.35-4.35"/></svg>
          <span class="search-label">Search</span>
          <kbd>⌘K</kbd>
        </a>
        <div class="theme-toggle" role="group" aria-label="Select theme">
          <button class="theme-btn" data-theme-value="light" title="Light mode" aria-label="Light mode">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 7a5 5 0 1 0 0 10A5 5 0 0 0 12 7zm0-2a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V2a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1zm0 14a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 2 0v-2a1 1 0 0 0-1-1zm9-8h-2a1 1 0 0 0 0 2h2a1 1 0 0 0 0-2zM5 12a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H2a1 1 0 0 0 0 2h2a1 1 0 0 0 1-1z"/></svg>
          </button>
          <button class="theme-btn" data-theme-value="dark" title="Dark mode" aria-label="Dark mode">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 3a9 9 0 1 0 9 9c0-.46-.04-.92-.1-1.36a5.389 5.389 0 0 1-4.4 2.26 5.403 5.403 0 0 1-3.14-9.8c-.44-.06-.9-.1-1.36-.1z"/></svg>
          </button>
          <button class="theme-btn" data-theme-value="auto" title="Auto (system)" aria-label="Auto theme">Auto</button>
        </div>
        <a class="github-btn" href="https://github.com/flaglint/flaglint" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="section-kicker">LaunchDarkly Node.js SDK to OpenFeature</div>
          <h1>Your LaunchDarkly contract<br>renews soon.</h1>
          <p style="font-size:clamp(18px,2.4vw,26px);font-weight:700;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.25;margin:-10px 0 20px;letter-spacing:-0.01em;">Do you know how hard it is to leave?</p>
          <p class="hero-sub">FlagLint audits every direct LaunchDarkly SDK call in your Node.js codebase, classifies migration risk, and generates OpenFeature rewrites only where safety can be proven.</p>
          <div class="command-card" aria-label="Primary command" style="margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:16px;">
            <span class="muted">$</span>
            <code>npx flaglint audit ./src</code>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-row" style="margin-bottom:20px;">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/docs/cli/audit">Run your first audit</a>
            <a href="/docs/tutorials/migrate-a-node-service" style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--muted);padding:10px 4px;">View a real migration</a>
            <a href="/docs/integrations/github-actions" style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--muted);padding:10px 4px;">Add it to CI →</a>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--subtle);">
            <span>MIT licensed</span>
            <span style="color:var(--border-strong)">·</span>
            <span>Node.js 20+</span>
            <span style="color:var(--border-strong)">·</span>
            <span>Runs locally</span>
            <span style="color:var(--border-strong)">·</span>
            <span>No API key</span>
            <span style="color:var(--border-strong)">·</span>
            <span>No source upload</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="proof-shell" aria-label="Audit output from enterprise checkout demo">
          <div class="terminal-header">
            <div class="dots" aria-hidden="true">
              <span class="dot red"></span><span class="dot yellow"></span><span class="dot green"></span>
            </div>
            <span class="term-version">flaglint v0.6.0</span>
          </div>
          <div class="terminal-body">
<pre><span class="muted">$</span> npx flaglint audit ./src
<span class="muted">- Auditing ./src...</span>

<span class="green">✓ Audit complete: 13 flags — 3 high risk, 10 medium, 0 low</span>

<span class="muted">Flag Key               Risk       Usages  Reasons</span>
<span class="muted">──────────────────────────────────────────────────────</span>
<span class="red">dynamic                🔴 High    7       dynamic key</span>
<span class="red">checkout-experiment    🔴 High    1       detail evaluation</span>
<span class="red">*                      🔴 High    1       bulk call</span>
<span class="amber">checkout-v2            🟡 Medium  1       safely automatable</span>
<span class="amber">payment-provider       🟡 Medium  1       safely automatable</span>
